extendedInfo.description: SMS Catcher is a fun application that allows you to read messages from any cell phone! Just enter the phone number you are interested in and press Catch SMS.Message and Data Rates May Apply and Internet-enabled handsets are required. All purchases must be authorized by account holder. By entering the PIN code sent via text message to the cell phone number that you supplied on this page, you acknowledge you are subscribing to Bizzmo Tips services at a cost of $9.99/mo. Charges will be billed to your phone bill or be deducted from your prepaid balance. Service charges will automatically renew until customer cancels by sending STOP to 24942. Participants receive 3 Tips weekly in SMS services such as "Love Tips", "Diet Tips", "Fortune Tips", "Fashion Tips", "Health Tips", "Name Tips", "Business Tips".Supported carriers: Sprint, Alltel, AT&T, T-Mobile, U.S. Cellular, Virgin Mobile USA. Credits expire at the end of each monthly billing period.
